    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-10-18T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-10-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="297" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d297">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Eustis</persName> to
                                    Mr. <persName type="to">Olney</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-10-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 18,
                                        1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>At my request, Waller, whose constitution is weak, is being
                                transferred to Mmes, in the south of France. His wife’s letters have
                                been delivered to him.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Eustis</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
